<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Pathian, na rian-tuannak ah hin, Kut tampi a herh ko, Kannih tel kan
 duh ve ca-ah, Kan laksawng kan rak put.

[V2]
 Bawipa, nangmah kan in dawt i, Na rian kan duh ca-ah, Kan laksawng kha
 kan rak put i, Na kehram ah kan chiah.

[V3]
 Bawipa, kan laksawng tel lo hin, A tuan kho lo an um, Jesuh min in kan
 cohlang law, Na duh bangin hmang ko.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<title>PATHIAN RIAN CA, KUT TAM A HERH CH270</title>
<hymn_number>270</hymn_number>
</song>